description: Hello! I'm passionate about learning and action, a graduate of the dynamic Soy Henry bootcamp in May 2023. Since then, I've been on a continuous journey of discovery and growth. I'm friendly and always ready to dive into new projects. My passions include video games, reading, soccer, and constant learning. I enjoy challenges and strive to give my best in everything I do. I'm currently actively seeking job opportunities where I can apply my skills and knowledge. My adaptability, responsibility, and flexibility make me a valuable asset to any team. Let's do amazing things together!
